data.description: Act fast 27 Forest Ridge Road is here. This charming large three bedroom, one-and-a-half-bathroom home is located in a quiet neighborhood. This recently renovated home boasts a spacious floor plan that is perfect for family living. Hardwood floors on the second level and a laundry room on the main level add a nice touch. There is plenty of closet space throughout and shed in the backyard for storage. One of the standout features of this unit is its easy access. Situated conveniently close to major highways, commuting to work. Whether you're heading downtown or planning a weekend getaway, you'll appreciate the effortless travel options available to you. Lots of work was recently done to this home including the installation of a brand-new solar panel. Schedule your private tour today, before it's too late.
